      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "I think Integer.MAX_VALUE an achievable value, so it can be matched by a representable number of digits.  This does not always matter as a larger figure is not possible as +1 would overflow to Integer.MIN_VALUE.  Never the less, it&#39;s not quite the same as Infinity?"
