    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Integer Infinity :</p>\n<pre><code>  Integer maxNumber = Integer.MAX_VALUE\n</code></pre>\n<p>Double Infinity</p>\n<pre><code>  Double maxNumber = Double.MAX_VALUE;\n  Double positiveInf = Double.POSITIVE_INFINITY;\n  Double negativeInf = Double.NEGATIVE_INFINITY\n</code></pre>\n<p>Float infinity</p>\n<pre><code>   Float positiveInf = Float.POSITIVE_INFINITY;\n   Float negativeInf = Float.NEGATIVE_INFINITY\n   Float maxNumber = Float.MAX_VALUE;\n</code></pre>\n"
